Characteristics for segments dataset:
segment_id
length
time (time duration of one segment)
speed:
  horizontal speed: mean, std, range
  vertical speed: mean, std, range
sinuosity: mean, std, range(difference between biggest and smallest)
acceleration: mean, std, range
slope: mean, std, range
tmode_manual

distance to train/tram/bus station


Optional (in discuss for further optimization/improvement)
(proportion of static points for train/tram/bus stops)
(average time duration of pause for train/tram/bus stops)
